    "text": [
        "Respected Sir,",
        "I, Rubina, student of fourth year Computer Science class in your esteemed institution, wanted to inform you that I am unable to complete my assigned project within last week.",
        "I was well aware about the deadline and was working very hard to finish it on time but unfortunately, I received the news of death of my grandfather. I had to rush to another city, Mumbai, immediately so that I can pay my last respects and be there with my family. Had it not been a sad moment for my family, I would have submitted the project by now.",
        "Sir, I am extremely very sorry for missing out the submission and would request you to please allow me some more time to finish the assignment. I had already finished drafting it and will surely formalize it within next week.",
        "I hope you will understand my situation and grant one week extension for the submission.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Rubina"
    ],
